{"tid":1406984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒野還燒野 但係唔該你地唔好係咁近民居燒啦屌","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:35:50.000Z","uid":68084,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86a293a57ff0a4021ccf905a5c52a22a26631286","tid":1406984,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"利申 本人絕對唔支持任何人縱火 , 危害到他人性命及財產就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋係犯法架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n     <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要燒出大路燒啦<br />\n<br />\n起馬D煙唔會直上民居先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好用膠制品同遮扔去燒 會有有毒氣體<br />\n<br />\n同埋物資好珍貴<br />\n<br />\n緊記千其唔好落油燒車啊!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n當你地連車都燒埋 消防唔係咁易救得熄架<br />\n<br />\n再者象徵意義上 燒車代表著呢場革命已經升級 無人可置身事外<br />\n<br />\n就算你人唔係到 你只要有任何係香港 財產物業一樣遭殃<br />\n<br />\n(客觀睇 大部分情況 其他國家真係有反對派軍閥同政府軍打緊仗先會有燒車情況出現)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者影到既話<br />\n<br />\n香港會正式變為不安全城市<br />\n<br />\n到時成個烏克蘭咁<br />\n<br />\n香港經濟正式GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收手啦各位 唔好癲到走去燒車啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地收手啦 唔好犯法啦 <br />\n<br />\n萬一演變到烏克蘭咁<br />\n<br />\n就番唔到轉頭架啦"},{"pid":"bf2796f5480f26ff2355874eaede838e7b86c3d6","tid":1406984,"uid":47042,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"唔講真係以為波斯富街過百粒TG 係空氣清新劑"},{"pid":"cd4d0b922e5c50ed3d0d3cf1cd165bec5f3024e2","tid":1406984,"uid":75619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"去太空示威啦，一定唔會影響到人"},{"pid":"2a92ccb3005d02eac5f8b36ed0f182cbc481d17f","tid":140698